name: Ja Ri Audiovisual Loop
description: A fragment from a collaboration between visual artist rollinos (@rollinos) and brazilian artist Jadsa (@jadsaaa). The 15 seconds loop is part of the visual work for 'Ja Ri', track from "Olho de Vidro", Jadsa's breakthrough first record released by Balaclava Records, it contains a fragment from Jadsa's song as well.  The work is commissioned by music video festival (www.musicvideofestival.com.br).
